>
  {/* Testimonial note (deck): confirm with author — "Google Apps" is the
      era-correct name for Google Workspace; quote trimmed with ellipses only. */}
  <Fragment slot="why">
    <p>
      Dual certification is rarer than it sounds — most providers push one platform because it’s
      all they know. We’ve migrated businesses in both directions for 18 years and will tell you
      plainly which fits.
      <a href="/why-one-partner/">See how one-partner technology works →</a>
    </p>
